Switch  Prodino0_ReleOut1  "Chiave"              <switch>       (gAlarmSystem, gMapDb, gHouseAlarm) ["Switch"] {ga="securitySystemArmed", channel="mqtt:topic:cm4home:prodino:output1", expire="1s,command=OFF"}
